commit.message:
Fix regression from ac2588c6 that caused missing translatable strings

We still need the `_p` tag for intltool, so validating the appstream file must be done on the generated file (for now). In the future we should migrate away from intltool which shouldn't be necessary any more (https://wiki.gnome.org/MigratingFromIntltoolToGettext)

verification.payload:
tree cfda542971ccca5991acf1f477efb9ad2ac72ee8

author Cameron White <cameronwhite91@gmail.com> 1711849450 -0400
committer Cameron White <cameronwhite91@gmail.com> 1711849450 -0400

Fix regression from ac2588c6 that caused missing translatable strings

We still need the `_p` tag for intltool, so validating the appstream file must be done on the generated file (for now). In the future we should migrate away from intltool which shouldn't be necessary any more (https://wiki.gnome.org/MigratingFromIntltoolToGettext)
